                    ðŸ”¹ Summary of Java 8 Features
                    -----------------------------
*   Feature	                                Description
    -------                                 -----------
1)  Lambda Expressions	                    Shorter way to write anonymous functions
2)  Functional Interfaces	                Interfaces with only one abstract method (@FunctionalInterface)
3)  Default & Static Methods	            Add methods in interfaces without breaking old code
4)  Stream API	                            Process collections efficiently (map(), filter(), collect())
5)  Method References	                    Use :: instead of lambda to call methods
6)  Optional Class	                        Avoid NullPointerException safely
7)  Collectors	                            Convert Stream results into collections
8)  Date & Time API	                        Modern API for dates (LocalDate, LocalTime, LocalDateTime)